				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Razing Sword of Skarlon = good sword<BR>
Nice blade. You have to get through FGs which are usually always taken if your on most servers. First Fire Giant spawn is 2 giants I'm pretty sure warriors. Depends who you are how good you are etc. My guild usually does with 2 full well rounded groups. Ench in this case is probably an essential to charm a giant as you cannot mez them. Next is more giants wizards then king tranix a tough sob too. For most I'd recomend 3+ groups of 45+ unless you do this about 5+ times a week and can do it in about an hour depending on the last time they were killed and how long they are spread out.<BR>
It's a good sword but in my opinion rather rare. Skarlon also drops Mithril Vambraces(10ac,+7str,+sv5magic)and Mithril Leggings(I believe it's the same except sv10magic).<BR>
I've been on ALOT of fg runs and I've never seen the sword drop. I heard it drop for a guild member a few times ago. But today we did twice back to back respawns and I got the vambraces the first time and a guild member got the leggings the second time. nada on the sword.<BR>
Eitherway a good sword but I hate to break it to you but a good chance your not gonna get until your low 40s(with a guild that twinks ya) to 50.<BR>
And then most guilds with any sense at all will give this to paladins and shadow knights as they cannot duel wield and warriors can. I'm a warrior and I'm up as soon as SKs and Pallies all have that can use(or that can use and are there since it's no drop).<BR>
<BR>
Good luck just remember better stuff in the planes.<BR>
